H0.text: What has a central vein called a midrib. Feather

H1.text: What has a central vein called a midrib. Fin

H2.text: What has a central vein called a midrib. Petal

H3.text: What has a central vein called a midrib. Leaf

A4.text: In pinnately veined leaves the central vein is known as the midrib.

A5.text: The secondary veins, also known as second order veins or lateral veins, branch off from the midrib and extend toward the leaf margins.
